{"text_id":62260,"tokens":["This"," paper"," presents"," a"," tool"," for"," addressing"," a"," key"," component"," in"," many"," algorithms"," for"," planning"," robot"," trajectories"," under"," uncertainty",":"," evaluation"," of"," the"," safety"," of"," a"," robot"," whose"," actions"," are"," governed"," by"," a"," stochastic"," process","."," We"," consider"," the"," safety"," of"," a"," robot"," as"," a"," function"," of"," time",","," and"," define"," this"," function"," in"," terms"," of"," the"," probability"," of"," the"," robot"," remaining"," in"," an"," arbitrary"," safe"," region"," of"," the"," workspace"," over"," any"," time"," interval","."," The"," resulting"," safety"," function"," is"," a"," natural"," choice"," for"," many"," applications",","," including"," applications"," that"," require"," evaluating"," the"," likelihood"," of"," collision"," with"," obstacles"," or"," other"," dynamic"," objects","."," The"," base"," of"," our"," approach"," is"," a"," novel"," continuous","-","time"," Markov"," chain"," model"," of"," the"," robot","'","s"," motion","."," This"," model"," captures"," the"," robot","'","s"," dynamic"," behavior",","," incorporates"," the"," effects"," of"," inputs"," to"," the"," robot","'","s"," actuators",","," and"," includes"," the"," possibility"," of"," random"," external"," disturbances","."," We"," formulate"," the"," robot"," safety"," function"," as"," the"," probability"," of"," remaining"," in"," a"," safe"," region"," over"," all"," time",","," conditioned"," on"," the"," robot","'","s"," initial"," state"," and"," its"," trajectory"," up"," to"," the"," present"," time","."," Our"," main"," result"," is"," a"," method"," for"," computing"," this"," safety"," function"," exactly"," and"," efficiently"," for"," a"," broad"," class"," of"," robot"," systems",","," including"," linear"," and"," nonlinear"," systems"," with"," Gaussian"," noise","."," We"," demonstrate"," our"," method"," on"," two"," examples",","," a"," un","icycle"," robot"," navigating"," in"," the"," presence"," of"," moving"," obstacles"," and"," a"," quadro","tor"," aircraft"," flying"," in"," an"," urban"," environment","."],"sub_source":"sci_gen","model":"text-davinci-002","label":1}